Dan<br>
Contact your Congressmen, most of them have a an individual that will help you get the necessary paper work completed and filed. Of course, sometimes when you do contact your congressmen and the military has to deal with them you get RED MARKED, your name goes up on their wall as a trouble maker.<br><br>
I contacted my congressmen last year, and the Corps did answered me right away after that, but, from then on every note or letter I wrote was personally looked over and  red lined to make sure I did things by the book. <br><br>
Hang in there buddy, we're here and many of us have gone through what you are going through,<br><br>
